    <section class="faq card" id="faq">
      <h2>FAQs</h2>
      <details>
        <summary>How do I set up business web calling?</summary>
        <p>Use SIP/VoIP providers with APIs to enable calling directly in your app or browser. Configure agents, forwarding, and call routing rules.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can I use one number for both SMS and calls?</summary>
        <p>Yes, many virtual numbers support both SMS and voice. Check provider capabilities by region and type of number.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>How does web messaging work?</summary>
        <p>Web messaging uses APIs to send/receive SMS, MMS, or chat messages via your app. Messages are delivered through programmable APIs to your server endpoints.</p>
      </details>
